1.title: Episode #1.1

episode of.title: Dumb Girls Don't Go to Heaven (TV Series 2008– )

1.plot: Candy is a beautiful young girl who marries the man she believes to be the love of her life, Patricio. Her happiness only lasts one day as on the same day of the wedding, Candy discovers her husband enveloped in a passionate kiss with her very own sister, Alicia. Stripping of her wedding dress and throwing it in his face, Candy leaves to find her destiny somewhere else. A few days later Candy finds out she is pregnant from the one night she was with Patricio.
